      "x": 16040,
      "y": 4100,
      "width": 1320,
      "height": 1220,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "n_attack_frontier_rationale_1",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "(ASR, evasion) Pareto-frontier geometry for \u00a74b-(II) \u2014 pure and model-free.  The.md",
      "x": 16060,
      "y": 4180,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 60
    },
    {
      "id": "n_attack_frontier_rationale_106",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "ASR achievable at a fixed ``evasion`` level, linearly interpolated.      Outside.md",
      "x": 16260,
      "y": 4180,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 60
    },
    {
      "id": "n_attack_frontier_rationale_56",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "Return the non-dominated set, deduplicated and ordered by evasion ascending..md",
      "x": 16460,
      "y": 4180,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 60
    },
    {
      "id": "n_attack_test_frontier_rationale_1",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "Tests for the (ASR, evasion) Pareto-frontier geometry (playbook \u00a74b-(II)).  Pure.md",
      "x": 16060,
      "y": 4260,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 60
    },
    {
      "id": "n_attack_frontier_rationale_47",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "True iff ``q`` Pareto-dominates ``p`` (= on both axes,  on at least one)..md",
      "x": 16260,
      "y": 4260,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 60
